"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b17.8.4'>Est 8:4</a></span></p></span></p>"},{"id":"peshitta-notas-1951","title":"Ester 4:14","author":"Instituto Cultural Álef y Tau, A.C.","reference":{"book":"EST","chapterStart":4,"verseStart":14,"chapterEnd":4,"verseEnd":14},"content":"<span style=\"color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\"><sup>a</sup></span> </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b3.26.42'>Lev 26:42</a></span>; </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b12.13.5'>2Re 13:5</a></span></p></span></p>"},{"id":"peshitta-notas-1952","title":"Ester 4:16","author":"Instituto Cultural Álef y Tau, A.C.","reference":{"book":"EST","chapterStart":4,"verseStart":16,"chapterEnd":4,"verseEnd":16},"content":"<span style=\"color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\"><sup>7</sup></span> </span><span style=\"\" lang=\"es-ES\">Lit.</span>, </span><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" lang=\"es-ES\">y si me matan</span>, </span><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" lang=\"es-ES\">que me maten</span><span style=\"\" lang=\"es-ES\">. Es decir</span>, </span><span style=\"\" lang=\"es-ES\">como en un sacrificio u ofrenda.</span></p><span style=\"color:#0000FF;\"></span></p><span style=\"color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\"><sup>a</sup></span> </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b9.19.4-5'>1Sa 19:4-5</a></span>; </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b44.20.24'>Hch 20:24</a></span></p></span></p>"},{"id":"peshitta-notas-1954","title":"Ester 5:3","author":"Instituto Cultural Álef y Tau, A.C.","reference":{"book":"EST","chapterStart":5,"verseStart":3,"chapterEnd":5,"verseEnd":3},"content":"<span style=\"color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\"><sup>a</sup></span> </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\